Welcome to biosim’s documentation!¶

This is a simulation of an island including

  • Herbivores

  • Carnivores

  • Several landscapes

  • An island

The animals module creates herbivores and carnivores.

The cell module creates cells, consisting of lowland, highland, desert and water. In the cell module we also include what happens in the cell, eg. feeding and procreation.

In the MapIsland module we create the island and put together all the cells. In addition it simulates everything that happens on the island during a year.

In the simulation module we simulate the whole island, including the visualisation.
